  "title": "Sourcing Executive / 5 days / Kallang - Electronics Firm",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Responsible for raw material sourcing by getting competitive quotes</p></li><li><p>Identify, assess and onboard new suppliers to expand the company's vendor base</p></li><li><p>Negotiate favourable pricing and terms with suppliers to achieve cost savings</p></li><li><p>Monitor supplier performance and quality to ensure timely delivery of materials</p></li><li><p>Collaborate cross-functionally with the production, engineering and finance teams</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate inventory records and optimise stock levels</p></li><li><p>Analyse market trends and explore new sourcing opportunities</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with procurement policies and procedures</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma holder</li><li>Minimum 1-3 years of experience in a procurement or sourcing role, preferably in the electronics manufacturing industry</li><li>Excellent negotiation and communication skills with the ability to build strong relationships with suppliers</li><li>Proficient in data analysis and inventory management</li><li>Problem-solving mindset and a keen eye for detail</li></ul><p><strong>________________________________________________________________________</strong></p><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume by clicking on <strong>“Quick Apply”</strong> or contact <a href=\"tel:6566 5498\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">6566 5498</a> for more details.</p><p><strong>Please provide following information in the resume for immediate processing</strong></p><p>1) Reasons for leaving current and/or last employment</p><p>2) Last drawn and/or current salary</p><p>3) Expected salary</p><p>4) Date of availability and/or Notice Period</p><p><strong>All applications will be treated in strictest confidence and only shortlisted candidates will be notified</strong></p><p><strong>Joni</strong></p><p><strong>EA License No: 03C5391</strong></p><p><strong>EA Reg No : R1106641</strong></p></p>",
